  "title": "Retail Sales Assistant (AWS + Quaterly Bonus)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Support sales performance, budgeting, retail operations, and administrative tasks.</p></li><li><p>Deliver quality customer service and assist with merchandising and promotional activities.</p></li><li><p>Ensure accuracy and proper handling of sales transactions and receipts.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain positive customer relationships, including providing updates on products and promotions.</p></li><li><p>Maintain store cleanliness and visual standards in accordance with company guidelines.</p></li><li><p>Manage stock levels according to company inventory policies and participate in regular stock takes.</p></li><li><p>Work collaboratively with the team to achieve sales targets and operational goals.</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Minimum secondary school qualification (or equivalent).</p></li><li><p>At least 2 years of relevant experience in a retail environment.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work effectively as part of a team and independently when required.</p></li></ul><p><br />HOW TO APPLY:</p><p>Interested applicants, please click on “Apply Now” and provide the below details in your resume.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Ang Ren Jing (Dino)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25146829</p>",
